    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉选举争议一个月后，美国扣押马杜罗飞机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/maduro-s-plane-seized-by-us-one-month-after-disputed-venezuela-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国认定委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的飞机的购买和运营违反了美国的制裁，因此扣押了该飞机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/maduro-s-plane-seized-by-us-one-month-after-disputed-venezuela-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯和拜登联手在劳动节闪电战中争取工会投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-biden-teaming-up-to-court-union-vote-in-labor-day-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯希望在劳动节期间访问两个关键的摇摆州，包括与总统乔·拜登联合出席竞选活动，以加强她在蓝领工人中的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-biden-teaming-up-to-court-union-vote-in-labor-day-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚宣布关键油田遭遇不可抗力，裂痕加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/libya-declares-force-majeure-on-el-feel-oil-field</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧佩克成员国权力斗争引发石油停产扩大，利比亚国有石油公司宣布关键油田埃尔菲尔（El-Feel）遭遇不可抗力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/libya-declares-force-majeure-on-el-feel-oil-field</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:20:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国以违反法律风险为由暂停向以色列发放 30 份武器许可证</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/uk-suspends-30-arms-licenses-to-israel-citing-risk-of-law-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·拉米表示，英国认为在加沙使用英国武器可能违反国际人道主义法，因此将暂停向以色列发放的 350 份武器许可证中的约 30 份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/uk-suspends-30-arms-licenses-to-israel-citing-risk-of-law-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 16:08:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰盟友预计伊朗将很快向俄罗斯运送导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/ukraine-allies-expect-iran-to-ship-missiles-to-russia-imminently</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，欧洲官员预计伊朗将很快向俄罗斯运送弹道导弹，此举可能引发乌克兰盟友的迅速反应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/ukraine-allies-expect-iran-to-ship-missiles-to-russia-imminently</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 15:21:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>愤怒的以色列人挑战内塔尼亚胡关于人质死亡的红线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/israel-hamas-war-outcry-over-hostage-deaths-shows-netanyahu-cost-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周末，六名以色列人质在加沙隧道中被发现遭枪杀后，以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡做了一件他在 11 个月的战争中从未做过的事 — — 他向遇难者家属道歉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/israel-hamas-war-outcry-over-hostage-deaths-shows-netanyahu-cost-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 15:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西法官批准禁止使用谷歌 X，与马斯克的矛盾进一步加深</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/brazilian-judges-ratify-ban-on-x-in-deepening-feud-with-musk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最高法院确认了一项命令，禁止埃隆·马斯克的社交网络 X 在巴西使用，并对那些不遵守命令使用虚拟专用网络 (VPN) 的人处以罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/brazilian-judges-ratify-ban-on-x-in-deepening-feud-with-musk</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:25:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯称美国钢铁公司应保持国内所有和经营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-to-say-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-and-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯将于周一访问匹兹堡期间表示，美国钢铁公司应该继续在国内拥有和运营，这是该公司拟定出售给新日本制铁公司的计划遭遇的最新阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/harris-to-say-us-steel-should-remain-domestically-owned-and-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:38:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极左翼领导人在州选举后成为权力掮客</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/wagenknecht-emerges-as-powerbroker-after-german-state-votes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管极右翼政党选择党在图林根州周日的州选举中获胜，萨拉·瓦根克内西特 (Sahra Wagenknecht) 和她新组建的极左翼联盟 BSW 将在阻止该党在该州执政方面发挥关键作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-02/wagenknecht-emerges-as-powerbroker-after-german-state-votes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:24:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
